00:30:03.460 --> 00:30:05.726
of support you give us as writers.

00:30:05.780 --> 00:30:06.230
When we're working
alone for five years,

00:30:07.930 --> 00:30:08.263
it's nice to know you're out there.

00:30:09.930 --> 00:30:10.930
Thank you.

